items.badge_description: At a new place and don't want to choose a pint of something you may not like? Grab a few tasters! Enjoy some small pours and then decide which to upgrade to a full pour. That's 240 checkins with the serving style of Taster. Try 5 more for Level 49!

Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 85 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%. Try 5 more for Level 18!

items.badge_name: Beyond a Shadow of a Stout (Level 3)
items.badge_description: We all love Stouts, and now we have a dedicated badge to celebrate your dedication to these dark, top-fermented beer in multiple variations, like Oatmeal, Milk and more! Which one will you start with? That's 15 different beers with the style of Stout. Try 5 more for Level 4!
Do you come from the land down under, where beer does flow, and men chunder? That's at least 275 different beers from Australia. Try 5 more for Level 56!

There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 70 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 15!

Porters and Stouts are rich with both history and flavor. Roasty, dark, and delicious, these two styles helped start it all. Thats 20 different beers with the style of Porter or Stout. Try 5 more for Level 5!

Wouldnt it be nice if milk stouts came directly from beer producing cows? While this unfortunately isnt the case (yet) they do have a full body and sweetness due to a larger amount of lactose and sugars. That's 5 different beers with the style of Milk / Sweet Stout. Try 5 more for Level 2!

items.badge_name: Beyond a Shadow of a Stout (Level 2)
items.badge_description: We all love Stouts, and now we have a dedicated badge to celebrate your dedication to these dark, top-fermented beer in multiple variations, like Oatmeal, Milk and more! Which one will you start with? That's 10 different beers with the style of Stout. Try 5 more for Level 3!

items.checkin_comment: Awsome beer on nitro! A real treat! Very smooth and velvety with great stout flavour not too heavy not too light.

items.badge_description: Supporting local breweries is what helps the craft beer scene grow. You obviously know this since youre enjoying the local flavor! Be sure to always drink locally.
It's time to give bottle shops some love by adding them as your purchased location. That's 5 check-ins with a purchased location! Tag 5 more to get to Level 2.

Round and round the wheel goes! Which style youll be drinking, nobody knows! Your desire to explore different styles is inspiring. Keep it up! That's a check-in to at least 10 different styles. Try 5 more for Level 3!

While spontaneity can be fun, sometimes you want to make sure your adventure will rock. Checkout the menu at an Untappd Verified Venue before visiting and know exactly whats on tap! That's 255 check-ins at venue that is verified.  Try 5 more for Level 52!

Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 365 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%.  Try 5 more for Level 74!
